-- Citic Securities sees parent's assets HK listing done this year
-- By Alison Lui
-- Fri Mar 28, 2014 12:04AM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, March 28 (Reuters) - CITIC Securities Co Ltd <600030.SS><6030.HK> expects the whole asset listing of its major shareholder CITIC Group Corp [CITIC.UL] to be completed this year, the chairman of China's biggest brokerage said on Friday.

The company also does not rule out the possibility of acquiring other Chinese brokerages, Chairman Wang Dongming told a news conference in Hong Kong.